               <p>WILLIAM THOMAS BROUGH. I am a <rs id="t18260406-281-viclabel1519" type="occupation">tailor</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260406-281-victim1525 t18260406-281-viclabel1519"></join>, and live in Bartholomew-close. This handkerchief is mine - I lost it between <placeName id="t18260406-281-crimeloc1520">Finsbury-square</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18260406-281-crimeloc1520" type="placeName" value="Finsbury-square"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18260406-281-crimeloc1520" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260406-281-off1517 t18260406-281-crimeloc1520"></join> and <placeName id="t18260406-281-crimeloc1521">Whitecross-street</placeName>
